         <h1 id="post-18">Accommodation</h1>
<div id="print_icon">
</div>

<!-- <br clear="all" /> -->
<hr class="h2" />
          <div class="storycontent">
            <p>We have picked some well equipped and conveniently located hotels for you. Therefore participants are welcome to <a href="http://www.berlin-tourist-information.de/international/tagungsveranstalter/i_tv_buchung_neu.php?sprache=english&amp;id=122" target="_blank">choose one of the hotels</a> (opens in a new window).</p>
